name: Chocolate Midnight Martini
prepTime: 2 minutes
cookTime: 0 minutes
portions: 1

ingredients:
  - (1 shot)	Espresso
  - (1.5 oz)	Vodka
  - (1 oz)	Kahlua
  - (1 oz)   	Creme de Cacao

steps:
  - Combine ingredients (except for espresso) in shaker
  - Pull shot, and add to shaker
  - Fill shaker with ice, and shake to chill
  - Serve in a chilled martini glass
